text: Anouar Ben Abdallah (born 20 June 1996) is a Tunisian handball player who plays for Étoile Sportive du Sahel and the Tunisian national team.2019 World Men's Handball Championship roster He participated at the 2017 World Men's Handball Championship.2017 World Championship roster ==References== Category:1996 births Category:Living people Category:Tunisian male handball players Category:Handball players at the 2014 Summer Youth Olympics
